00:19:05.501 --> 00:19:08.341
salah.

00:19:11.341 --> 00:19:12.261
Ini berarti..

00:19:12.981 --> 00:19:14.261
Anda mencoba mengatakannya

00:19:14.741 --> 00:19:17.341
Ingatan Neeti..
- Ya.

